&lt;a class="linkcard-a" href="https://www.nqou.net/2026/01/30/000910/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" title="https://www.nqou.net/2026/01/30/000910/" aria-label="https://www.nqou.net/2026/01/30/000910/"&gt;
